@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam dpi 150

actor Guest as G
rectangle "Guest / Visitor Use Cases" {
  usecase UC1 as "Browse Landing & Choice Pages"
  usecase UC2 as "Search Clinics"
  usecase UC3 as "View Posts & Reviews"
  usecase UC4 as "Listen to Background Music"
  usecase UC5 as "Contact Support / View FAQs"
  usecase UC6 as "Register / Start Signup"
}

G --> UC1
G --> UC2
G --> UC3
G --> UC4
G --> UC5
G --> UC6

note right of UC4
  Music persists across PJAX navigation
  via single audio element + localStorage
end note

@enduml
